        FAQ2QC5.setFont(new java.awt.Font("Microsoft JhengHei UI", 0, 16)); // NOI18N
        FAQ2QC5.setText("<html>There are no restrictions on the number of pets you can carry on Emirates flights. However, please be aware that some countries do impose restrictions on the number of pets that can be carried into or out of the country. For example, the import of animals into India is restricted to two pets per customer. We advise you check your destination’s rules before travelling.<br><br>\n\nA maximum of two adult animals of comparable size weighing up to 14kgs each may be shipped in the same container, providing they are used to cohabitation. Animals weighing over 14kgs each must travel in separate containers.");
